  <description type="morphology">Stems nearly glabrous proximally to densely tomentose distally. Leaves 15–30 ×
        10–18 cm. Inflorescences with branches spreading to commonly drooping. Flowers erect; tepals
        deep green to yellowish green, 5–12 mm. 2n = 32.</description>
